{"tid":2316964,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"含會通過禁足令","createTime":"2020-12-08T08:42:30.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-08T16:23:26.000Z","uid":45910,"like":6,"dislike":140,"uniUserReply":54,"replies":[{"pid":"683da80bf23fa691c933fe64d8f56e8e8253c2af","tid":2316964,"uid":45910,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-12-08T08:42:30.000Z","msg":"食物及衞生局局長陳肇始表示，政府早前一直與律政司探討封鎖檢測的法律框架，今早框架獲行會通過。食衞局長將可發出《限制檢測宣告》，要求檢測人士，在有檢測結果前留在原本處所內，而<span class=\"red\">政府亦可以按需要，要求轉移處所</span>，或轉移到檢測中心，當有檢測結果後，便可以撤銷封鎖，封鎖時間最長為 7 日。<br />\n<br />\n她又指，部分有特殊需要人士可以申請離開，但仍要遵守相關規定，而社署及民政署會提供物資上的支援。社署將提供如梳洗物品、睡袋等物品。<br />\n<br />\n食物及衞生局常任秘書長陳松青解釋，執行時會把告示展示在處所出入口，「立即生效」，亦會委任包括執法人員在內的公職人員協助執行，限制任何人士離開或進入處所，要求處所內人士接受檢測等。<br />\n<br />\n記者會直播：<a href=\"https://bit.ly/36VMUxs\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F36VMUxs&d=JQtp7%2BScZlazt5%2F0T0af7DvkInyplymEwWc8t9jwBTE%3D&h=e3316bcd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/36VMUxs</a>"},{"pid":"273a16dacfbf3aecb59d3ee9c7f9af21bef2033e","tid":2316964,"uid":45910,"like":188,"dislike":2,"score":186,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-12-08T08:43:25.000Z","msg":"我懷疑你確診武漢肺炎，轉移去新屋嶺<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"322cbd42deab93295e1b717381ac367694afb26f","tid":2316964,"uid":25858,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"quote":{"pid":"273a16dacfbf3aecb59d3ee9c7f9af21bef2033e","tid":2316964,"uid":45910,"like":188,"dislike":2,"score":186,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-12-08T08:43:25.000Z","msg":"我懷疑你確診武漢肺炎，轉移去新屋嶺<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-08T08:45:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2d0a7545ed4c7b8b8f8c89466e64d118829e933d","tid":2316964,"uid":45910,"like":90,"dislike":0,"score":90,"citedBy":